I'd look out for you.

41:13.240 --> 41:15.160
And I let that get in my head,

41:15.160 --> 41:17.740
and it almost cost us
what we have here.

41:17.740 --> 41:19.410
So now, I'm gonna
look out for you

41:19.410 --> 41:21.830
in the way that I should have
in the first place.

41:21.830 --> 41:23.920
How's that?
By telling you the truth.

41:23.920 --> 41:27.170
They beat us at our own game,
Samantha.

41:27.170 --> 41:29.290
Whether we like it or not.

41:30.590 --> 41:32.590
But you know what that means?

41:34.470 --> 41:38.720
We are surrounded by
some badass people.

41:38.720 --> 41:40.310
So let's stop fighting in here

41:40.310 --> 41:43.430
and start fighting
everyone else out there.

41:44.810 --> 41:47.230
Because it's time to make peace.

41:48.190 --> 41:50.400
<i>♪ ♪</i>

41:51.280 --> 41:52.740
ALEX: Am I interrupting?

41:55.280 --> 41:58.620
Because I wanted to say
Harvey gave me the news, and...

41:58.620 --> 42:01.490
I'm good with it if you are.

42:04.040 --> 42:06.460
Of course I am, partner.

42:06.460 --> 42:10.000
Then I guess there's only
one thing to figure out.

42:10.000 --> 42:13.630
Williams Wheeler
or Wheeler Williams?

42:15.420 --> 42:16.930
You won, Alex.

42:16.930 --> 42:18.590
It's your choice.

42:20.180 --> 42:22.720
So, what do you say
we have ourselves

42:22.720 --> 42:25.480
a good old-fashioned group hug?

42:27.440 --> 42:32.980
<i>♪ I can feel it coming
In the air tonight ♪</i>

42:33.860 --> 42:35.860
<i>♪ Oh, lord ♪</i>

42:37.530 --> 42:40.660
<i>♪ And I've been waiting
For this moment ♪</i>

42:40.660 --> 42:43.490
<i>♪ For all my life ♪</i>

42:43.490 --> 42:45.960
<i>♪ Oh, lord ♪</i>

42:47.080 --> 42:49.250
Harvey, it's been a long day.

42:49.250 --> 42:50.920
So if you're here
to yell at me...

42:50.920 --> 42:54.210
Relax, Louis,
I'm here to say thank you.

42:54.210 --> 42:58.090
We lost ourselves,
and you brought us back.

42:59.340 --> 43:01.470
Thanks, Harvey.
I appreciate that.

43:01.470 --> 43:04.520
It takes a lot of balls to come
at me and Robert like that.

43:04.520 --> 43:06.230
No, Harvey, it didn't.

43:06.230 --> 43:08.190
Because for the first time,

43:08.190 --> 43:10.730
I didn't care how
either one of you saw me,

43:10.730 --> 43:13.820
because I didn't even care

43:13.820 --> 43:15.900
to be managing partner
in the first place.

43:15.900 --> 43:17.650
What do you mean?

43:19.030 --> 43:20.780
I'm gonna have a baby, Harvey.

43:22.700 --> 43:24.200
I'm gonna be a dad.

43:24.200 --> 43:27.080
And once that hit me,

43:27.080 --> 43:30.290
dealing with this
felt so simple.

43:31.250 --> 43:32.790
Congratulations, Louis.

43:34.380 --> 43:37.130
I think you are gonna make
a great managing partner,

43:37.130 --> 43:40.890
and I know you're gonna make
an outstanding father.

43:44.180 --> 43:45.970
You two need to get a room,

43:45.970 --> 43:48.310
or does anybody wanna
go out and celebrate?

43:48.310 --> 43:51.600
Actually, I think I'm just
gonna stay here for a bit

43:51.600 --> 43:52.860
and take it all in.

43:54.110 --> 43:55.940
I understand.

43:55.940 --> 43:57.240
Good night, Louis.

43:57.240 --> 43:58.780
Good night.

44:02.070 --> 44:04.200
HARVEY:
Level with me.

44:04.200 --> 44:05.950
You really think
he can handle this?

44:05.950 --> 44:08.750
I think desperate times
require desperate measures.

44:08.750 --> 44:10.210
And I think something else too.

44:10.210 --> 44:12.790
What's that?
I am going to enjoy

44:12.790 --> 44:15.040
