take orders from Louis.

44:15.040 --> 44:17.590
We're not gonna be the only
ones he's in charge of.

44:17.590 --> 44:19.590
He'll be giving you
plenty of orders too.

44:19.590 --> 44:21.510
No, he won't.
You're forgetting,

44:21.510 --> 44:23.220
[WHISPERS]
I'm the Louis whisperer.

44:23.220 --> 44:25.300
Are you sure about that?
When he walked in,

44:25.300 --> 44:27.390
he said you weren't
pulling it off, he was.

44:27.390 --> 44:29.640
[NORMALLY] Who do think
told him to say that?

44:29.640 --> 44:31.020
Holy shit.
Are you saying

44:31.020 --> 44:32.730
you're the real
managing partner?

44:32.730 --> 44:35.770
I'm not saying that, but
I'm also not not saying that.

44:35.770 --> 44:38.820
Come on, pretty.
Drinks are on you.

